rows.label: qst400205_msg0002
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ] Uh-oh. Maybe talking to a Superbian
soldier was a bad idea...

rows.label: qst400205_msg0003
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling ]Um, I had something to
ask, but I've completely
forgotten what it was...

rows.label: qst400205_msg0004
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ] Yes, asking an Imperial soldier
probably wasn't the best idea...

rows.label: qst400205_msg0005
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling ]I had something to ask, but
I'm sure you must be busy!

rows.label: qst400205_msg0006
rows.name:
Hmph. If it's information you
want, go ask the local informant.

rows.label: qst400205_msg0007
rows.name: Our job isn't to stand around and chat.
